rpc.model.util
Class ModelSupport

java.lang.Object
  rpc.model.util.ModelSupport

public class ModelSupport
extends java.lang.Object

ModelSupport is a data structure that consists of all units, all possible dependencies in that space of units, information about potential causes, caches that store the standardization of units, and which units have been marked as dependent or independent.
